test: add end-to-end daemon smoke tests (he-ofv)

Create smoke_test.go with test doubles for all external dependencies
(LLM provider, memory stores, channels) to verify the full daemon
wiring path without real postgres, APIs, or external services.

Tests:
- TestSmokeEndToEnd: message → assembler → agent → LLM → response
- TestSmokeWithMemoryContext: verifies memory blocks/STM inject into
  the system prompt sent to the LLM
- TestSmokeToolExecution: LLM requests tool call → agent executes →
  returns final response
- TestSmokeRouterIntegration: full path through router with mock channel

Test doubles:
- mockProvider/capturingProvider/toolCallingProvider (LLM)
- stubBlockRetriever/stubSTMRetriever/stubLTMSearcher (memory)
- mockChannel (channels)
